ygData.subject: Re: [EverQuest] List been quiet lately
ygData.msgSnippet: I ve got a 56 wood elf warrior...it s a GREAT combo! Str isn t as big an issue as you think...the higher dex and agi keeps her out of danger. She s got 162 str
ygData.messageBody:
I've got a 56 wood elf warrior...it's a GREAT combo! Str isn't as big an issue as you think...the higher dex and agi keeps her out of danger. She's got 162 str with kinda bad gear, and will have better once I invest in some better rings.  Heck of a lot easier on the eyes than a fatty, too.
----- Original Message -----
From: Rob LeBeau
To: EverQuest@yahoogroups.com
Sent: Thursday, June 27, 2002 2:02 PM
Subject: Re: [EverQuest] List been quiet lately

Did I read that right
A wood elf Warrior?  WOW
That is a rare choice.

How do you like playing this char?  do you find the
str difference as a hinderence?

Rob

P.S. Trying to keep messages going for the people
reading........lol
